006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.binding.metaschema;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.MarkupLine;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.MarkupMultiline;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.ObjectUtils;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.IBindingContext;
012import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.AbstractBoundModule;
013import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.IBoundModule;
014import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.MetaschemaModule;
015
016import java.net.URI;
017import java.util.LinkedHashMap;
018import java.util.List;
019import java.util.Map;
020
021import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
022
023@MetaschemaModule(
024    fields = {
025        UseName.class,
026        Remarks.class,
027        ConstraintValueEnum.class
028    },
029    assemblies = {
030        METASCHEMA.class,
031        InlineDefineAssembly.class,
032        InlineDefineField.class,
033        InlineDefineFlag.class,
034        Any.class,
035        AssemblyReference.class,
036        FieldReference.class,
037        FlagReference.class,
038        AssemblyModel.class,
039        JsonValueKeyFlag.class,
040        GroupingAs.class,
041        Example.class,
042        Property.class,
043        JsonKey.class,
044        AssemblyConstraints.class,
045        FieldConstraints.class,
046        FlagConstraints.class,
047        ConstraintLetExpression.class,
048        FlagAllowedValues.class,
049        FlagExpect.class,
050        FlagIndexHasKey.class,
051        FlagMatches.class,
052        TargetedAllowedValuesConstraint.class,
053        TargetedMatchesConstraint.class,
054        TargetedExpectConstraint.class,
055        TargetedIndexHasKeyConstraint.class,
056        KeyConstraintField.class,
057        TargetedIsUniqueConstraint.class,
058        TargetedIndexConstraint.class,
059        TargetedHasCardinalityConstraint.class,
060        MetaschemaModuleConstraints.class,
061        MetaschemaMetaConstraints.class,
062        MetaschemaMetapath.class,
063        MetapathContext.class
064    })
065public final class MetaschemaModelModule
066    extends AbstractBoundModule {
067  @NonNull
068  private static final MarkupLine NAME = MarkupLine.fromMarkdown("Metaschema Model");
069
070  @NonNull
071  private static final String SHORT_NAME = "metaschema-model";
072
073  @NonNull
074  private static final String VERSION = "1.0.0-M2";
075
076  @NonNull
077  private static final URI XML_NAMESPACE
078      = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(URI.create("http://csrc.nist.gov/ns/oscal/metaschema/1.0"));
079
080  @NonNull
081  private static final URI JSON_BASE_URI
082      = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(URI.create("http://csrc.nist.gov/ns/oscal/metaschema/1.0"));
083
084  @NonNull
085  private static final Map<String, String> NAMESPACE_BINDINGS;
086
087  static {
088    Map<String, String> bindings = new LinkedHashMap<>();
089
090    NAMESPACE_BINDINGS = bindings;
091  }
092
093  public MetaschemaModelModule(
094      @NonNull List<? extends IBoundModule> importedModules,
095      @NonNull IBindingContext bindingContext) {
096    super(importedModules, bindingContext);
097  }
098
099  @Override
100  public MarkupLine getName() {
101    return NAME;
102  }
103
104  @Override
105  public String getShortName() {
106    return SHORT_NAME;
107  }
108
109  @Override
110  public String getVersion() {
111    return VERSION;
112  }
113
114  @Override
115  public URI getXmlNamespace() {
116    return XML_NAMESPACE;
117  }
118
119  @Override
120  public URI getJsonBaseUri() {
121    return JSON_BASE_URI;
122  }
123
124  @Override
125  public MarkupMultiline getRemarks() {
126    return null;
127  }
128
129  @Override
130  public Map<String, String> getNamespaceBindings() {
131    return NAMESPACE_BINDINGS;
132  }
133}
